{
  "stem": "15768.2",
  "chunk_idx": 2,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 3.5,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "And whenever I asked, what is it that you do when you go into this little booth, they always said, it's a secret.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "And not until I was much, much older, I realized what they were telling me that they were telling secrets rather than keeping this as a secret from me.",
      "word_count": 29
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "But at the time, I was really very hurt.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "And I felt very left out, because that wasn't explained to me.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "Nevertheless, the school experience was good.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "My French became very fluent.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "And also, we learned Flemish at the same time, which is a, a blend of Dutch and French and German.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "And we had to learn both languages.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "So it was a bit tough coming in there.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "But of course, under no circumstance did I ever want to even let it be known there was German in my background.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "It was not popular to be German in any shape, for, or fashion, really.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "And in Brussels, we lived in a very small apartment.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "At that point, my mother was not well.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "And along with going to school, I did all the housekeeping and the shopping.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 27,
      "text": "I was old enough now to take over.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 28,
      "text": "And it was interesting.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 29,
      "text": "We, we cooked a single burner and only had cold water on the tap, which had to be boiled in order to clean the dishes.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 30,
      "text": "It wasn't the easiest way of learning housekeeping.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 31,
      "text": "But so it was.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 32,
      "text": "And that was for, for nine months.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 33,
      "text": "In the spring in April, early April, we were called to, to Antwerp to the American consulate, where finally our papers from the United States had been processed.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 34,
      "text": "We went through rigorous physical health examinations and--",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "This was done at the American consulate.",
      "word_count": 7
    }
  ],
